{"tid":348594,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"到底翠華有咩好食","createTime":"2017-08-05T23:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T10:48:50.000Z","uid":108120,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"709a4fd132667b79428ec76c5c88318132265af3","tid":348594,"uid":108120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T23:28:30.000Z","msg":"冇咩特別 唔係好好食 仲要咁貴<br />\n點解會吸引到d人專登黎香港食翠華🤔"},{"pid":"f0f8a4c2142312cd80e37b3d2c49d0f8b37fcc82","tid":348594,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:05:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇咩特別 唔係好好食 仲要咁貴<br />\n點解會吸引到d人專登黎香港食翠華🤔</blockquote><br />\n因為旅遊書介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你睇台灣pixnet十個嚟香港九個半都食，仲係專登去果隻"},{"pid":"e7358279218a66652aaf1efc0ee771bb1313ad97","tid":348594,"uid":42815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T03:23:11.000Z","msg":"事實上係無野特别好食"},{"pid":"6414dfb719bfcdcef801c521cde9a78bcfe64058","tid":348594,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:04:53.000Z","msg":"茶餐廳野可以點特別好食丫"},{"pid":"1faea67309ed40b0c2c8d45657247fc34072d3e4","tid":348594,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:35:53.000Z","msg":"你話我味覺差又好，我覺得翠華真係算好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好耐未食過正既銀芽肉絲炒麵，有次係翠華叫左，真係超正! <br />\n<br />\n同埋翠華真係唔算好貴，同埋d野食基本無伏，有次食個好似100樓下既魚扒餐，浸味同銀鱈魚一樣! 超好食，同埋又湯又奶油豬又一大pat菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa8423183a2e2159790ca13895bed8edfef6b10","tid":348594,"uid":47378,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:45:46.000Z","msg":"唔係話冇好食過佢又平過佢既餐廳，<br />\n之不過伏既餐廳更多<br />\n<br />\n你係遊客都唔想冒險啦<br />\n一間差既茶記係可以差到破壞你成日心情"},{"pid":"dfc9e5d248d11318bba987a77e2cd42230cdda71","tid":348594,"uid":44814,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:48:34.000Z","msg":"平時返工lunch都會食<br />\n起碼環境好先 無個啲大汗地盤佬 多數OL西裝友<br />\n另外味道好過好多茶餐廳先<br />\n奶茶幾啱我飲"},{"pid":"351781d2ea704fee9b510e1b826aea7f1fd9c8a3","tid":348594,"uid":124087,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時返工lunch都會食<br />\n起碼環境好先 無個啲大汗地盤佬 多數OL西裝友<br />\n另外味道好過好多茶餐廳先<br />\n奶茶幾啱我飲</blockquote><br />\n又歧視大汗地盤佬？大汗得撚罪你？死港女！"},{"pid":"8728fe21a7c0790cdc203f9ef8ee4ac337314024","tid":348594,"uid":50818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:00:05.000Z","msg":"翠華根本無任何野食<br />\n而且唔係做香港人生意<br />\n就算有野食都唔會再去"},{"pid":"891b1631f6a454ded003d2821a7a01d1e98ef8e5","tid":348594,"uid":44814,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:08:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平時返工lunch都會食<br />\n起碼環境好先 無個啲大汗地盤佬 多數OL西裝友<br />\n另外味道好過好多茶餐廳先<br />\n奶茶幾啱我飲</blockquote><br />\n又歧視大汗地盤佬？大汗得撚罪你？死港女！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀屌你 要搭枱真係仆街 伏過一獲 啲口水噴撚到埋黎<br />\n放工搭地鐵上遇著個大汗逼係你隔離都屌啦下話<br />\n我都係想舒舒服服食餐lunch姐 <br />\n點呀 臭汗味撈口水送飯？你食飽佢"},{"pid":"b9dd01f95247ae9e1095caf86d0c07af06740ccb","tid":348594,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"旅遊書介紹親既野都貴架啦"},{"pid":"14bb5e9fd70854bd1cfa20b060a041428e2741a8","tid":348594,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:10:17.000Z","msg":"咁係好少少ga 😋<br />\n不過窮閪食唔起😞"},{"pid":"645dd83006a8721ea208ce16b7fd1f8a33220d3f","tid":348594,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:11:51.000Z","msg":"海南雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過個飯唔得"},{"pid":"eca41efbd25b68d891eb124c472d34e4afc0615b","tid":348594,"uid":124087,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:12:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平時返工lunch都會食<br />\n起碼環境好先 無個啲大汗地盤佬 多數OL西裝友